description:
PLEASE READ location clarification! Convenient and cozy Queens location (NOT Manhattan). Grocery shops, bars, pharmacy around the corner. 15-20 min away from Manhattan in 7 express train, LIRR, M and R trains. 

Lots of restaurants in diverse, safe, quiet and local neighborhood.

It's a sanctuary from the intensity of the City while traveling for work or fun. It's conveniently located, easy access to Manhattan and calm and quiet as well.

My landlord is very delicate about keeping the building clean and safe which I truly appreciate. So think about this place as a comfortable getaway and be as discrete, quiet and respectful as possible.

hosts.about: I am a ballet teacher for children and dancer from Guatemala living in New York for the last 6 years.  My apartment is my sanctuary and I take care of it because I know what it takes to live in this City.  I can't live without family, friends, art, chocolate and wine. I want to travel soon to Barcelona, Mexico, Greece and Iceland. I love jazz, nice people and good vibes.
